  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Fluorinated gases and ozone-depleting substances: how to do business in the transition period
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How businesses can continue to trade and deal in fluorinated gases (F gas) and ozone-depleting substances (ODS) in the UK and EU during the transition period.</p>

  </div>
</div>

