<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="reporting-your-f-gas-activity">Reporting your F gas activity</h2>

<p>F gas regulation will remain the same during the transition period. This means you must continue to operate as you did before 31 January 2020.  This means that you must:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/ods2/resources/domain/resolve" class="govuk-link">report your F gas activities from 1 Jan 2019 to 31 December 2019</a> to the European Commission by 31 March 2020</li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/ods2/resources/domain/resolve" class="govuk-link">report your F gas activities from 1 Jan 2020 to 31 December 2020</a> to the European Commission by 31 March 2021</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="f-gas-qualifications-and-company-certification">F gas qualifications and company certification</h2>

<p>Qualification and certification requirements for working with F gas will remain the same. Your qualifications will still be recognised throughout the EU during the transition period.</p>

<h2 id="reporting-your-ods-activity">Reporting your ODS activity</h2>
<p>ODS regulation will remain the same during the transition period. You must continue to operate as you did before 31 January 2020.  This means you must:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/ods2/resources/domain/resolve" class="govuk-link">report your ODS activities from 1 Jan 2019 to 31 December 2019</a> to the European Commission by 31 March 2020.</li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/ods2/resources/domain/resolve" class="govuk-link">report your ODS activities from 1 Jan 2020 to 31 December 2020</a> to the European Commission by 31 March 2021.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="other-activities">Other activities</h2>

<p>All other parts of the regulation continue to apply as normal. Read:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/fluorinated-gas-f-gas-guidance-for-users-producers-and-traders" class="govuk-link">fluorinated gas (F gas): guidance for users, producers and traders</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/ozone-depleting-substances-guidance-for-users-producers-and-traders" class="govuk-link">ozone-depleting substances: guidance for users, producers and traders</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
